title: The emergent genetic future of Parkinson's
itunes:title: The emergent genetic future of Parkinson's
description: Dr. James Beck, Chief Scientific Officer at the Parkinson’s Foundation, talks with Daniel about the role genetics can play with Parkinson’s, a progressive neurologic disorder with no known cause, and which affects nearly one million people in America.
author: CVS Health
